# Ybx1 rescue primers for DNA

This document contains information about constructs that will be used for profiling DNA inserts of the rescue constructs for YB-1 engineered in the piggyBac vectors.

## Individual constructs

These are the sequences of the EFS promoter and the rBG poly-A sequence that we will prime off of. These will be the basis for our primer design. For primer design, I am using the [PrimerBlast](https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/tools/primer-blast/index.cgi) tool from NCBI.
